     /home/tom/Development/zkhydra/bugs/zkbugs/dataset/circom/succinctlabs/telepathy-circuits/trailofbits_incorrect_handling_of_point_doubling_can_allow_signature_forgery/circuits/pairing/bigint.circom:453:5

         ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ The assigned signal `div[k]` is not constrained here.

         ------------------- The signal `div[k]` is constrained here.
